languages.text: "Паршиво выглядишь, Мейв. Амасека что ль перебрала? Впрочем, ты не одна тут такая. Иди проспись, мой тебе совет".

traits.locale_text: "Паршиво выглядишь, Мейв. Амасека что ль перебрала? Впрочем, ты не одна тут такая. Иди проспись, мой тебе совет".

languages.text: "You look like crap, Maive. One amasec too many, huh? Well, it's not like you're the only one. Here's my advice: go have a good sleep."

languages.text: "Berbat görünüyorsun Maive. Amaseki fazla mı kaçırdın? Ben de. Sana bir tavsiye: Güzel bir uyku çek."
languages.original_text: "You look like crap, Maive. One amasec too many, huh? Well, it's not like you're the only one. Here's my advice: go have a good sleep."

traits.locale_text: "Berbat görünüyorsun Maive. Amaseki mi kaçırdın? Ne diyeyim, yalnız değilsin. Benden sana bir tavsiye: Güzel bir uyku çek."

languages.text: «Maive, tienes un aspecto penoso. Te has pasado con el amasec, ¿no? Bueno, tú y todos. Te daré un consejo: vete ya a la cama».
languages.original_text: "You look like crap, Maive. One amasec too many, huh? Well, it's not like you're the only one. Here's my advice: go have a good sleep."

traits.locale_text: «Maive, tienes un aspecto penoso. Te has pasado con el amasec, ¿no? Bueno, tú y todos. Te daré un consejo: vete ya a la cama».

languages.text: “你脸色可真差，梅芙。艾玛赛克酒喝得太多了，是吧？哈，喝多的人可不止你一个。要我说嘛，只要好好睡一觉就好了。”
languages.original_text: "You look like crap, Maive. One amasec too many, huh? Well, it's not like you're the only one. Here's my advice: go have a good sleep."

traits.locale_text: “你脸色可真差，梅芙。艾玛赛克酒喝得太多了，是吧？哈，喝多的人可不止你一个。要我说嘛，只要好好睡一觉就好了。”

languages.text: « Vous avez une mine affreuse, Maive. Vous avez un peu trop forcé sur l'amasec ? Ma foi, vous êtes loin d'être la seule. Un conseil : une bonne sieste, et il n'y paraîtra plus. »

languages.text: "Ihr seht schrecklich aus, Maive. Zu viel Amasec, was? Tja, da seid Ihr in guter Gesellschaft. Schlaft Euren Rausch einfach aus."
